					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13416534#post-4682736</guid>
				<title>Re: I don&#039;t need sleep, I need awnsers</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13416534/scp-5937#post-4682736</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2020 17:41:23 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>RockTeethMothEyes</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4022320</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Hi! I'm glad you liked the article.</p> <p>I don't intend to expand more on this. When I brought this to reviewers, they each had different conclusions about what is going on here, and only after posting did people reach the conclusion I intended. Furthermore, I feel as if giving away much more than what I have would lead to showing too much and detracting satisfaction from solving the puzzle as laid out.</p> <p>So, no one gets answers. And I think thats fine.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13416534#post-4682524</guid>
				<title>I don&#039;t need sleep, I need awnsers</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13416534/scp-5937#post-4682524</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2020 14:01:54 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Desiderium</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6526025</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I liked this very much, but I feel like I need more awnsers. I mean, he said he was aware of the effects since january of 2018. Does this means he felt the box growing inside him? Did he manage to open it up by accident? He used the screwdriver to open it? But if he did so why hide the screwdriver inside it? Or it was someone else opening the box?</p> <p>Are you going to write more? Because I need awnsers!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
